      <title>紐西蘭航空將從芬蘭 Neste 購買綠色燃料以實現淨零排放目標</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-buy-green-fuel-finlands-neste-meet-net-zero-targets-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[紐西蘭航空週一與芬蘭煉油商 Neste 簽署了最大的永續航空燃料 (SAF) 協議，以脫碳並實現其淨零碳排放目標。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-buy-green-fuel-finlands-neste-meet-net-zero-targets-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:20:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度法院廢除舊制度後，莫迪警告政治資金中存在“黑錢”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-warns-black-money-political-funding-after-old-system-scrapped-by-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度總理莫迪在周一播出的演講中表示，最高法院決定廢除有爭議的政治資助制度，導致政黨捐款流向「黑錢」或非法資金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-warns-black-money-political-funding-after-old-system-scrapped-by-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:05:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
