      <title>FBI 對巴爾的摩大橋倒塌事故展開刑事調查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/fbi-opens-criminal-probe-into-maryland-bridge-collapse-washington-post-says-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[聯邦調查局週一表示，該局已對上個月巴爾的摩一座大橋發生致命倒塌事件展開聯邦刑事調查，當時一艘船撞上了其中一個支撐物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/fbi-opens-criminal-probe-into-maryland-bridge-collapse-washington-post-says-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 11:46:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列表示，它與美國「並肩」擊落了伊朗的齊射飛彈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-it-shot-down-iranian-salvo-shoulder-to-shoulder-with-us-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列高級官員表示，以色列擊退伊朗大規模無人機和飛彈齊射的行動是與五角大廈充分協調的，五角大廈在「箭」彈道防空系統的控制室裡設有一名美國作戰聯絡官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-it-shot-down-iranian-salvo-shoulder-to-shoulder-with-us-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 11:22:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪梨三天內發生第二起刺傷事件，多人受傷</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/several-people-injured-stabbing-sydney-church-police-say-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方和目擊者稱，週一悉尼郊區一座教堂舉行儀式時發生持刀襲擊，造成包括一名主教在內的至少四人受傷，引發憤怒的居民與警方之間的衝突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/several-people-injured-stabbing-sydney-church-police-say-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 10:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
